Chisinau by the ngo Centre of Information and Resources PRO BONO in collaboration with the National Youth Council of Moldova, the Chisinau city Hall and Mayor of Tohatin. Being founded on 9 December 2017, TohaTEEN Hub aims to help young people in the Environment and in the adjacent localities to develop personally and to contribute to the development of the community of which they are part.
